                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "fc23049dfb2d4f609cfbd",
                    "stepText": "Next, identify the correct formula used to calculate radiated intensity from a black body according to the Stefan-Boltzmann law. Please choose the right expression.",
